title: Core Death Overcast
description:
Core Death - Overcast
www.coredeath.com

Eighteen electronica tracks released by Core Death. Album encompasses many different sub-genre&#039;s of electronic music including:

Ambient, Acid, Trance, IDM (Intelligent Dance Music), Rock, Drum and Bass, Breakbeat, Classical, and Industrial.

Core Death has been influenced by many different artists, such as:

Crystal Method, Evil Nine, Aphex Twin, Roni Size, Tiesto, Benni Benassi

TRACKLISTING
1. Ambiental Experience.mp3
Ambient/chillout track, slow and great for background music

2. Acid Tripin.mp3
Retro acid sounding track

3. BLT Trance.mp3
Simple trance song using real drums

4. Cheesehead.mp3
An IDM track influence heavily by Aphex Twin.

5. Wrath.mp3
Slow/sad guitar track. Guitar played by The Terrains

6. Wedge.mp3
Fast drum and bass track.

7. The Hand that Feeds.mp3
Remix of The Hand That Feeds by Nine Inch Nails.

8. Requiem for an Illusion.mp3
Drum and bass track influenced by the movie "Requiem for a Dream". Uses vocals by Sandy from the song Illusion by Benni Benassi.

9. Patrolman.mp3
Gritty, almost ambient electronic track.

10. Bodyguard.mp3
Ambient, almost tribal electronic track.

11. Intermission.mp3
Short song using guitar played by Terrains.

12. 5th Symphony.mp3
Experiment using the notes of Fifth Symphony.

13. Desperate Times.mp3
Ambient

14. Dreaming.mp3
Psychedelic

15. Brooklyn.mp3
Four to the Floor

16. Diligence.mp3
Industrial track, the most intricate of the album

17. Platonic.mp3
Slow, ambient, piano 

18. Elation.mp3
Slow, ambient, synthetic

Download includes front and back cover art and a 1600x1200 wallpaper.
